title: High kick! Million Dollar Listings, Contingencies and a Renovation from Hell
itunes:title: High kick! Million Dollar Listings, Contingencies and a Renovation from Hell
itunes:subtitle: So what’s the deal with brick from Chicago, anyway?
description:
This week, Madi and Aleena swap roles as Aleena pretends she’s a badass boss like Tracy Tutor (from Million Dollar Listing: Los Angeles) and schools the team on typical real estate practices, this wild pandemic housing market and how the hell someone could reasonably risk putting in a $6 million offer on a house - sight unseen.
